        <abstract> 
<p>Orders a copy of September number of <hi rend="italic">Silliman’s Journal</hi>. A friend has recommended an article in it [A. Gray and D. Treadwell, "Discussion between two readers of Darwin’s treatise on the origin of species", <hi rend="italic">Am. J. Sci.</hi> 2d ser. 30 (1860): 226–39].</p> 
